text: I tried their sushi platter and it was pretty good. The portion was enough and the staff were very friendly. Overall, the food was tasty. Will try their hot food next time!
1st time buying sushi and they do not give the soy sauce. Had to purchase at $0.10 each. Unless i had purchase a big box. Small minded business and Inflation sucks.
Umisushi is located in Eunos MRT, just follow the unit number to find. Small shop with limited seating capacity. Friendly staff and the portion of food just nice.

This is the 2nd time I've ordered from this branch and I'm utterly disappointed. The first time I ordered the cup corn and it was sourish (after which I had food poisoning) and today the kani mayo sushi turned bad... I won't order from them ever again
service staff were nice but the sushi is terrible.... the rice is so soggy it's like the wet glue used for craft..... not worth the price for a convenient sushi takeout
